---
import BaseHead from '@/components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '@/components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '@/components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Cookie Policy — Alex Morcillo" description="Learn about how this website uses cookies, what types are used, and how to manage your cookie preferences." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
			<p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-ink-muted dark:text-cream-muted mb-6 animate-fade-up">
				Legal
			</p>
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
				Cookie Policy
			</h1>
			<div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-accent my-8 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s"></div>

			<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
				<p>
					In compliance with Article 22.2 of Law 34/2002, of July 11, on Information Society Services and Electronic Commerce (LSSI-CE), we inform you about the cookie policy of this website.
				</p>

				<h2>What Are Cookies?</h2>
				<p>
					Cookies are small text files that websites store on your device (computer, mobile phone, tablet) when you visit them. They are used to make the website function properly, to improve the browsing experience, and to provide information to the site owners.
				</p>

				<h2>What Types of Cookies Do We Use?</h2>

				<h3>Technical Cookies (Required)</h3>
				<p>
					These cookies enable navigation through the website and the use of the various options or services it offers. They are essential for the proper functioning of the site.
				</p>

				<h3>Analytics</h3>
				<p>
					This website uses <strong>Plausible Analytics</strong>, a privacy-friendly analytics service. Plausible does not use cookies, does not collect personal data, and does not track you across websites. All data is aggregated and no individual visitors can be identified. For more information, visit <a href="https://plausible.io/data-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Plausible's data policy</a>.
				</p>

				<h3>Third-Party Services</h3>
				<p>
					This website may use third-party services that could log access data:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Google Fonts:</strong> for loading typefaces. Google may log access data.</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>How to Manage Cookies</h2>
				<p>
					You can allow, block, or delete cookies installed on your device by configuring your internet browser settings:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Google Chrome:</strong> Settings &rarr; Privacy and Security &rarr; Cookies and Other Site Data</li>
					<li><strong>Mozilla Firefox:</strong> Options &rarr; Privacy &amp; Security &rarr; Cookies and Site Data</li>
					<li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences &rarr; Privacy &rarr; Cookies and Website Data</li>
					<li><strong>Microsoft Edge:</strong> Settings &rarr; Cookies and Site Permissions &rarr; Cookies and Stored Data</li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					If you disable cookies, some website features may not be available or may not function correctly.
				</p>

				<h2>Cookie Policy Updates</h2>
				<p>
					This cookie policy may be updated at any time. We recommend reviewing this policy each time you visit our website.
				</p>

				<p class="font-mono text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-cream-muted">
					Last updated: March 2026
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
